_sText:
This is an ak-colt map, meaning that the terrorist start with ak's and the CT's start with m4a1's. It has 64 spawns but I would only recommend playing 16 on 16 max.

Please don't criticize the water until you have actually played the map and looked at it. 

All constructive criticism is appreciated, and I hope you like the map. The Map looks a lot nicer in-game also.

Have fun, enjoy, and always look both ways before crossing the street,
DoF 

Please tell me if you add this to your server, because I will stop by and play a few games!!!! Thanks!
